Dog Trainer

Our dog trainer will ensure your pup can do the most challenging tricks. You will be so proud that you might consider enrolling your dog in America’s Got Talent.

Professional Trainers to unlock your dog's potential

Dog Walker

Our dog walkers know the best trails for your dog. We make sure trials do not have nasty burrs that get stuck in dog paws or furs. At the end of all walks, the walker will provide a complimentary butt and paw massage to loosen the muscles.

1 - 1 walks only 

Dog Companion

Our dog companions are not any regular dog sitters. We will make sure your dog is very relaxed and happy. While we are with your dog, we have extensive tests to figure out what activities your dog enjoys. Snacks and meals are all inclusive. Only Evian water is served. (Bubbly water for an additional fee).

Evian or specially filtered water

For an additional fee, you can pick and choose whether you want your human companion for your dog to wear certain clothing, use your soap/lotion/shampoo so the human companion smells like you. This is recommended if you plan to leave your dog for more than 3 days to minimize anxiety.

Ensuring your pup is in good hands

Dog Whisperer

Miss your dog that passed away? Don’t despair! Our dog whispers can channel your dog and let you know how they are doing. They can also rely any messages you have for them. Most of our clients have recurring annual sessions on their dog’s birthday to let them know they haven’t forgotten and miss them.

Dog whisperer

Dog Massage Therapist

Want to make sure your pup is stress free and enjoys life to the fullest? Perhaps you want that little extra to spoil your furry one. Our dog massage therapists are licensed massage therapists that specialize working with dogs. They know all the sore and pressure points.

Finest natural and organic spa treatment

Dog Acupuncturist

Got a dog that has smelly breath, snores or a bad leg? 

Our dog acupuncturists have techniques to alleviate those symptoms.

Acupuncture is often used to treat dogs with arthritis and joint inflammation.
Best doctors and natural medicine for your dog
